[h3 id=Tricks
 
	" Tricks
	$LF
]h3
[h4 id=Transitionburst
 
	" Transition burst
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"When entering the boss screen, we loose control of the character. However, we can still act during the first frame of the screen. Bursting during this first frame allows us to get closer to the boss during the cutscene. On some bosses, this trick is not possible, but it is still possible to burst at the last frame of the previous screen for a similar effect.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=Cancels
 
	" Cancels
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"There are several cancels and resets among Plague's list of movements:
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Normally, Plague can throw 3 bombs then there's a cooldown until he can throw a bomb again. The double jump resets the cooldown, so he can throw 6 bombs rapidly
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" The Burst can be canceled by an item
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" The end of the Staff item animation can be canceled by a double jump
		$LF
	]li
]ul
